name: Emilia
message:
Greetings from Carolina! I'm bored to tears at work so I decided to check 
out your blog on my iphone during lunch break. I enjoy the info you provide here and can't wait to 
take a look when I get home. I'm shocked at how fast your blog loaded on my phone ..
I'm not even using WIFI, just 3G .. Anyhow, awesome blog!
